=== {{GBR}} ===
2011年4月28日，在[[英国|英国]][[剑桥公爵威廉王子与凯特·米德尔顿的婚礼|剑桥公爵威廉王子与凯特·米德尔顿的婚礼]]前夕，因為全国镇压政治活动，数个有政治动机的Facebook群组和专页从网站被移除或中止。这些群组和专页大都关注反对政府削减开支，许多延续{{link-en|2010年英国学生抗议|2010 UK student protests}}，用来举办示威活动<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/apr/29/facebook-activist-pages-purged |title=Activists claim purge of Facebook pages |last=Malik |first=Shiv |date=2011-04-29 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2013-12-10 |location=London |language=en |trans_title=积极分子称Facebook专页遭清除 |archive-date=2013-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720012407/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/apr/29/facebook-activist-pages-purged |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Facebook 'suspends UK activist groups' |url=http://www.channel4.com/news/facebook-suspends-uk-activist-groups |accessdate=2011-10-29 |date=2011-04-29 |publisher=Channel 4 News |language=en |trans_title=Facebook“中止英国积极分子群组” |archive-date=2011-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110903124202/http://www.channel4.com/news/facebook-suspends-uk-activist-groups |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/04/29/facebook-deactivates-protest-pages-in-britain/?partner=rss&emc=rss |title=Facebook Deactivates Protest Pages in Britain |last=Preston |first=Jennifer |date=2011-04-29 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2013-12-10 |language=en |trans_title=Facebook停用英国抗议页面 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809080332/https://mediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/04/29/facebook-deactivates-protest-pages-in-britain/?partner=rss&emc=rss |dead-url=no }}</ref>。页面的审查与一系列积极分子被捕时间恰逢<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/apr/29/royal-wedding-police-criticised-protesters |title=Royal wedding: police criticised for pre-emptive strikes against protesters |first=Robert |date=April 29, 2011 |work=The Guardian |last2=Laville |first2=Sandra |location=London |language=en |last3=Malik |first3=Shiv |last1=Booth |trans_title=皇族婚礼：警方被批评打击示威者 |accessdate=2013-12-11 |archive-date=2011-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501084857/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/apr/29/royal-wedding-police-criticised-protesters |dead-url=no }}</ref>。被捕当中包括正策划雕像斩首表演以反对君主制的街头戏剧团体，其中成员包括66岁的[[人类学|人类学]]教授<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-13234682 |title=Royal wedding: Three held over effigy beheading claims |date=2011-04-29 |work=BBC News |accessdate=2013-12-10 |language=en |trans_title=三人因声称将雕像斩首而被捕 |archive-date=2019-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190801131451/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-13234682 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
=== {{VNM}} ===
